友孫、皆可慾淫。弱女信徒，秘書病人，或其親朋子侄，無一倖免。女盜口穴逢迎，奪夥計貞操。師者巨乳貶壓，誘學子心性。亦不然，交合時暗錄活春宮，分別時皇皇然脅之，又得幾回歡愉。女甫口角，輒奔舊愛，哭啼哭啼，又變嘿咻嘿咻。男欲內發，女言不可，搖頭嗔目，元陽閉穴。」此之謂也。"},{"pid":"3154afe694a890cf13620b90ecc3c5685f89cf0d","tid":723353,"uid":45120,"like":3,"dislike":11,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T11:07:20.000Z","msg":"睇錯大小便通吃"},{"pid":"faf8a93e97ddff81b7d6bb2c4804e76866081cdc","tid":723353,"uid":59898,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T11:17:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"048ed27ef1b2e264a48c563d34e5ff2ca653d578","tid":723353,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T11:35:29.000Z","msg":"好有錢都好難母女通吃，前世做好多好事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee9b0a72f785404b211e7dfd4619525e842d1ff0","tid":723353,"uid":72009,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T11:36:44.000Z","msg":"義女: 我緊Ｄ定媽媽個臭西緊Ｄ"},{"pid":"9fea83972458579421a664b166838b6e89eb6dd5","tid":723353,"uid":2429,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"048ed27ef1b2e264a48c563d34e5ff2ca653d578","tid":723353,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T11:35:29.000Z","msg":"好有錢都好難母女通吃，前世做好多好事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T11:47:03.000Z","msg":"仲要13歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f604f17df1cd446dbfab61b1e163f71d3378d2d5","tid":723353,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"9fea83972458579421a664b166838b6e89eb6dd5","tid":723353,"uid":2429,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"048ed27ef1b2e264a48c563d34e5ff2ca653d578","tid":7233